<p>Set <span class="command">Single Word Justification</span> to <span class="command">Align Left</span>.</p>

<p>These numbers are a starting point. Theyâ€™re not written in stone. Theyâ€™re better than what Adobe set as defaults, but if they donâ€™t work for you, adjust them.</p>

